{{en-noun}}

# {{context|nautical|lang=en}} A single-masted [[sailboat]] with only one [[headsail]].
#* '''Year?''', Olaudah Equiano or Gustavus Vassa, ''The Interesting Narrative of the Life of Olaudah Equiano'',
